1
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:32,320
♪During the dark night♪

2
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:34,940
♪A guiding light♪

3
00:00:34,940 --> 00:00:36,920
♪Just like you♪

4
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:42,290
♪Makes life turn bright♪

5
00:00:42,550 --> 00:00:47,540
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

6
00:00:47,540 --> 00:00:51,130
♪You gave me strength♪

7
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:53,810
♪Running for truth♪

8
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:58,440
♪I find my path♪

9
00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:03,090
♪Drawing on the hope♪

10
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:06,740
♪That you render me♪

11
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,870
♪In this long journey♪

12
00:01:09,870 --> 00:01:13,940
♪I run on lightly♪

13
00:01:30,820 --> 00:01:33,120
=Reborn=

14
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:35,080
(Adapted from the serialized work "Reborn"
by Qiang Yu)

15
00:01:35,642 --> 00:01:36,282
It's all right.

16
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,310
You're not as pretty as your sister,

17
00:01:38,310 --> 00:01:39,080
but I like

18
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:40,640
that uptight attitude of yours.

19
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,510
Your sister was...

20
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:42,310
Shut up!

21
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:43,670
I won't.

22
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,440
Do you know what she was like?

23
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,950
Especially after a few drinks.

24
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,920
She'd do anything you tell her to do.

25
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,470
Let me go!

26
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,030
She has a cutter!

27
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,200
I've already called the police.

28
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,470
Let's get out of here, Hei.

29
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:31,000
I'll be back.

30
00:02:31,017 --> 00:02:33,385
♪Maybe♪

31
00:02:35,014 --> 00:02:40,508
♪We were afraid of losing♪

32
00:02:42,117 --> 00:02:47,388
♪So our steps kept hesitating♪

33
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,160
Are you all right?

34
00:02:48,497 --> 00:02:53,905
♪But you're the shadow I can't escape♪

35
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:12,660
♪Turns out, all my thoughts♪

36
00:03:12,982 --> 00:03:14,911
♪Spell your name♪

37
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:15,960
It's okay.

38
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,280
I'm here for you.

39
00:03:18,288 --> 00:03:23,445
♪The one and only stubbornness
in my heart♪

40
00:03:23,911 --> 00:03:27,280
♪Thankfully, we were naive enough♪

41
00:03:27,348 --> 00:03:30,720
♪And brave just in time♪

42
00:03:30,831 --> 00:03:39,002
♪To make sure our moments
weren't lost to time♪

43
00:03:39,025 --> 00:03:46,030
=Episode 8=
(It's Okay. I'm Here for You.)

44
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,440
Mom. Dad. Have some tea.

45
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,520
(Fang Yanqiu: Where are you?)

46
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,750
(Fang Yanqiu: Where are you?)

47
00:04:17,751 --> 00:04:21,180
(Incoming call from Mr. Sun)

48
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:22,670
Yes?

49
00:04:22,990 --> 00:04:24,200
Is this Mr. Ming?

50
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,800
Ming Sheng got into some trouble
at school.

51
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,320
You're an embarrassment.

52
00:04:49,230 --> 00:04:49,960
Mrs. Qiao.

53
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:53,080
I apologize
for the trouble caused, Mr. Sun.

54
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:54,960
Please calm down.

55
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,030
Let me introduce.

56
00:04:56,230 --> 00:04:58,080
This is Qiao Qingyu's mother.

57
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,110
You're here, Mr. Ming.

58
00:05:01,110 --> 00:05:02,430
Mr. Sun. Director.

59
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,350
Do you two know each other?

60
00:05:10,470 --> 00:05:11,280
No, we don't.

61
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,670
You're Qiao Qingyu's mother?

62
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,470
I'm Ming Sheng's father.

63
00:05:15,670 --> 00:05:16,400
Nice to meet you.

64
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:19,910
What happened?

65
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:22,880
I believe Mr. Sun already explained
the situation to you both.

66
00:05:24,110 --> 00:05:25,230
Mrs. Qiao.

67
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,400
The incident at the school gate

68
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,550
is still under investigation.

69
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:31,550
The group of delinquents involved
have been taken to the police station.

70
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:33,280
It has caused a very negative impact.

71
00:05:33,670 --> 00:05:36,230
Qiao Qingyu has an older sister,
correct?

72
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:38,200
We have heard about that as well.

73
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,790
The school sympathizes
with what your family has gone through.

74
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,880
But the incident today
still reflects poorly on us.

75
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:45,960
So,

76
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:48,350
please talk to Qingyu when you get home.

77
00:05:48,350 --> 00:05:51,160
Have her reflect on her actions
over the next few days and stay home.

78
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:54,280
Sir, I apologize on her behalf.

79
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,230
She's still a child.
She doesn't know any better.

80
00:05:56,230 --> 00:05:57,990
As her mother,
I didn't raise her well enough.

81
00:05:57,990 --> 00:05:59,350
I know she was wrong.

82
00:05:59,350 --> 00:06:00,790
I apologize to you,

83
00:06:00,790 --> 00:06:03,670
to her teachers,
and to everyone at the school.

84
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:05,590
But she is a good kid
who loves studying.

85
00:06:05,590 --> 00:06:07,230
You have to let her stay in school.

86
00:06:07,230 --> 00:06:09,200
Can't you give her another chance?

87
00:06:13,990 --> 00:06:15,840
My injury had nothing to do
with Qiao Qingyu.

88
00:06:16,910 --> 00:06:18,670
I accidentally cut my hand

89
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:20,350
when I borrowed her cutter.

90
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:22,110
It was all just a misunderstanding.

91
00:06:22,110 --> 00:06:23,720
Ming Sheng.

92
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,910
That is a bold claim to make.

93
00:06:24,910 --> 00:06:26,840
Others are saying something else.

94
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,430
Sir, I'm not making anything up.

95
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,640
And I was directly involved.

96
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:31,910
So I know exactly

97
00:06:31,910 --> 00:06:33,280
how it happened.

98
00:06:33,590 --> 00:06:33,990
You...

99
00:06:33,990 --> 00:06:37,550
Sir, those troublemakers

100
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:39,160
have already been detained

101
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,670
for causing a public disturbance.

102
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:43,400
The ringleader will be held for a while.

103
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,840
They all have criminal records.

104
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,350
They regularly harass girls.

105
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:49,670
Qiao Qingyu was a victim, too.

106
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,230
We can't punish the victim

107
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:53,230
just because of the actions

108
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:54,430
of a few thugs.

109
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,790
If word got out,

110
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:57,640
people would say

111
00:06:57,640 --> 00:07:00,110
our school can't tell right from wrong.

112
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:00,910
Sir,

113
00:07:01,670 --> 00:07:04,110
Qiao Qingyu had nothing to do
with Ming Sheng's injury

114
00:07:04,110 --> 00:07:05,910
and the whole incident.

115
00:07:05,910 --> 00:07:06,590
There's no reason

116
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:08,350
for the school to punish her.

117
00:07:09,790 --> 00:07:10,590
I have heard

118
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:13,350
some rumors

119
00:07:13,590 --> 00:07:15,030
about Qiao Qingyu's sister.

120
00:07:15,590 --> 00:07:16,910
As a medical professional,

121
00:07:17,590 --> 00:07:18,720
I urge the school

122
00:07:18,990 --> 00:07:21,110
to improve education on these matters.

123
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,790
So that ignorance does not cause

124
00:07:23,790 --> 00:07:25,230
unnecessary fear or stigma.

125
00:07:26,470 --> 00:07:27,110
Right.

126
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,470
All right, Mrs. Qiao.

127
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:31,400
We'll stay in touch.

128
00:07:33,910 --> 00:07:35,520
Qingyu, you really need

129
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,590
to learn from this.

130
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,320
If something like this
ever happens again,

131
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,590
tell a teacher or a parent

132
00:07:39,590 --> 00:07:40,520
right away.

133
00:07:40,990 --> 00:07:42,760
Don't just charge in
on your own like that.

134
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:44,760
You're still a minor.

135
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,670
It's our job as adults to protect you.

136
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,470
Do you understand?

137
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,790
So the school is not punishing me?

138
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,400
Ming Sheng already explained everything.

139
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,880
It was just an accident.

140
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,990
The school has no reason to punish you.

141
00:07:59,910 --> 00:08:01,080
Mr. Sun, we'll head home now.

142
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,320
All right. Take care on the way.

143
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:05,320
Mrs. Qiao, please go easy on her.

144
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:09,760
Go home with your mother.

145
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,790
All you do is humiliate us!

146
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:37,880
Why did you help Qiao Qingyu

147
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,830
at school today?

148
00:08:40,310 --> 00:08:41,520
Didn't you want to help her?

149
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,760
She's your friend.

150
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,190
I figured she couldn't be all that bad.

151
00:08:47,950 --> 00:08:49,400
Be careful not to get your wound wet.

152
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,120
Stay home for the next couple of days.

153
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,070
Stay here.

154
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,120
I can take care of you.

155
00:08:57,340 --> 00:09:00,690
(Incoming call: Fang Yanqiu)

156
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,550
Why won't you answer your phone?

157
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,160
Am I interrupting?

158
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:14,830
No, it's nothing important.

159
00:09:14,830 --> 00:09:15,910
I'll call back later.

160
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:19,030
What do you want for dinner?

161
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,840
I'll make it for you.

162
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:22,600
Anything's fine.

163
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:40,910
Qingyu,

164
00:09:41,710 --> 00:09:44,910
I think Mom's chopping you up

165
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:47,830
like dumpling filling over there.

166
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,670
Come on, tell me.

167
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,880
Were you really planning
to stab that punk

168
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:54,950
with the cutter?

169
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:58,030
You're so cool.

170
00:09:58,030 --> 00:10:00,480
You're a real hero.

171
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:04,710
I heard
you accidentally hurt Ming Sheng too.

172
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:07,310
He's usually so tough,
but he didn't come after you.

173
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:09,310
Did he hit his head or something?

174
00:10:25,310 --> 00:10:26,240
(It's okay.)

175
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,670
(I'm here for you.)

176
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,550
Ming Sheng.

177
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,310
Ming Sheng.

178
00:10:58,910 --> 00:10:59,600
Dinner's ready.

179
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:13,520
Hello?

180
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:16,030
Is this Dr. Ming?

181
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:17,120
He's cooking.

182
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,830
Oh, it's you, Ming Sheng.

183
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:21,190
This is Ms. Zhang
from the neighborhood committee.

184
00:11:21,190 --> 00:11:23,030
Your dad mentioned he wanted to donate

185
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:25,160
some sheet music
to the community center.

186
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:27,190
I was wondering
if he has sorted them out yet?

187
00:11:27,190 --> 00:11:27,880
Sheet music?

188
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,120
What's the meaning of this?

189
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:47,950
Your mom told me

190
00:11:47,950 --> 00:11:49,480
she didn't need those anymore

191
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,880
and asked me to take care of them.

192
00:11:52,190 --> 00:11:53,120
I get it.

193
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:55,240
Just trying
to clear out some space, right?

194
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:56,600
Don't worry.

195
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:58,670
Mom and I won't get in your way.

196
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:00,910
Ming Sheng.

197
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:06,520
Ming Sheng.

198
00:12:08,190 --> 00:12:08,760
Ming Sheng!

199
00:13:10,070 --> 00:13:12,160
It's the middle of the night.
Why are you still up?

200
00:13:13,310 --> 00:13:14,670
We gave them the wrong names.

201
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,000
Huh?

202
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,950
We have to change Qing's name.

203
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:20,640
Why?

204
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,600
I asked around.

205
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,830
Qiao Beiyu. Qiao Qingyu.

206
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,430
It's unlucky to give girls
the "Yu" character.

207
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:30,790
They'll be hard to raise.

208
00:13:31,830 --> 00:13:32,880
We already lost Bei.

209
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,430
I'm scared we'll lose Qing too...

210
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,910
Nonsense!

211
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,710
Stop making trouble where there is none.

212
00:13:40,030 --> 00:13:41,920
You think you own the police station
or something?

213
00:13:41,920 --> 00:13:43,720
You can change things
just because you say so?

214
00:13:44,310 --> 00:13:45,400
Go to bed.

215
00:14:03,830 --> 00:14:06,430
Something happened
with Ming Sheng at school yesterday.

216
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:08,000
I really couldn't get away.

217
00:14:08,400 --> 00:14:09,030
I'm very sorry.

218
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:12,160
You already explained everything
on the phone yesterday.

219
00:14:12,190 --> 00:14:12,880
I understand.

220
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:15,600
Of course, your son comes first.

221
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,760
That's not what I meant.

222
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,600
How about dinner tonight

223
00:14:26,190 --> 00:14:27,600
with your parents?

224
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:31,120
They have already gone back to our hometown.

225
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,480
We'll talk about it another time.

226
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,160
Yanqiu.

227
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:42,400
I...

228
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:42,880
Yanqiu.

229
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,240
The nursing department needs you.

230
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:46,430
Coming.

231
00:14:54,310 --> 00:14:55,600
Everyone,

232
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:58,030
finish these problems
before the teacher gets here.

233
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:01,560
Just thinking about those arrogant jerks

234
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:02,920
from No.1 High School makes me mad.

235
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,480
If Ming Sheng hadn't missed the game,

236
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,640
we wouldn't have lost to them.

237
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,480
Drop it. We had issues too.

238
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,070
What?

239
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,830
Look at his hand.

240
00:15:14,310 --> 00:15:15,400
It looks serious.

241
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,790
Will it leave lasting damage?

242
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:20,550
Qiao Qingyu.

243
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,480
Ming Sheng wouldn't have hurt his hand
if it weren't for you.

244
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,480
And we would have won.

245
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:26,030
Apologize to Ming Sheng.

246
00:15:34,910 --> 00:15:35,760
Do it!

247
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,280
Is it that hard to say sorry?

248
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,950
Or do you still think
you did nothing wrong?

249
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,240
Just apologize.

250
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:53,280
It was your fault.

251
00:15:54,430 --> 00:15:55,430
Give it a rest.

252
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,640
Whether Qiao Qingyu apologizes or not

253
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:59,120
is between the two of us.

254
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,910
Stay out of this.

255
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,520
Quiet!

256
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:05,000
It's self-study time.

257
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:05,760
Got it.

258
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:38,600
Are you okay?

259
00:16:38,710 --> 00:16:39,910
Did you see who did it?

260
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:40,910
That was so messed up.

261
00:16:41,830 --> 00:16:42,950
I didn't,

262
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:43,950
but I know who did it.

263
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:50,310
Did you see Qiao Qingyu's face?

264
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,550
Wish I could've gotten it on camera.

265
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:55,280
Do you think she knows it was us?

266
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:57,910
What is she going to do? Tell on us?

267
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,310
She has no proof.

268
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:25,510
Qingyu,

269
00:17:25,670 --> 00:17:27,320
did they give you any more trouble?

270
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:28,910
No.

271
00:17:29,430 --> 00:17:31,910
The head of the discipline
already talked to them.

272
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,400
They apologized to me too.

273
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:36,120
Thanks.

274
00:17:37,910 --> 00:17:38,800
No problem.

275
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:49,840
Here.

276
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,120
It's for you.

277
00:17:55,430 --> 00:17:58,600
You were the one spying on me dancing
that day, weren't you?

278
00:18:19,542 --> 00:18:23,857
♪Under the sunlight♪

279
00:18:24,010 --> 00:18:26,620
♪Birds take flight♪

280
00:18:26,848 --> 00:18:33,237
♪Raise me up, hold me high♪

281
00:18:35,482 --> 00:18:39,882
♪During the dark night♪

282
