297
00:19:19,670 --> 00:19:20,400
Come on, Qing.

298
00:19:21,320 --> 00:19:22,510
Lift your arm,

299
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:25,470
then raise them.

300
00:19:34,670 --> 00:19:36,670
You were amazing, Qing!

301
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:41,910
Qing. Qing?

302
00:19:42,990 --> 00:19:43,800
Qingyu.

303
00:19:45,430 --> 00:19:46,190
Qingyu?

304
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,190
