Go ahead.

319
00:20:17,470 --> 00:20:19,430
Chaoyang New Village.

320
00:20:21,270 --> 00:20:24,600
Unit 806, Building 13.

321
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:26,560
One order of fried noodles,
no spice, right?

322
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:28,230
Got it. Order's on the way.

323
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:30,360
I'll deliver that, Qiao Huan.

324
00:20:30,360 --> 00:20:31,800
Aren't you going to the library?

325
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:33,040
It's on my way.

326
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:34,190
All right.

327
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:00,160
Delivery.

328
00:21:01,600 --> 00:21:03,510
Delivery from Qiao's Noodle Shop.

329
00:21:11,990 --> 00:21:14,040
We have a new promotion going on.

330
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:15,160
Let me tell you about it.

331
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:15,840
I don't need it.

332
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,880
You always order from us.

333
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:18,750
You'll want this deal.

334
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:19,750
I said I don't need it.

335
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:20,990
It'll only take a moment...

336
00:21:24,430 --> 00:21:25,120
Ow...

337
00:21:25,670 --> 00:21:26,560
What's your deal?

338
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:44,400
You're usually a tough guy at school.

339
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:46,230
Didn't expect you
to be such a mess at home.

340
00:21:46,230 --> 00:21:48,040
I'd love for the others
to see this side of you.

341
00:21:48,190 --> 00:21:49,560
Seriously?

342
00:21:50,190 --> 00:21:51,160
Who do you think

343
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,600
is the reason I'm in this state?

344
00:21:52,710 --> 00:21:53,510
Huh?

345
00:21:58,600 --> 00:21:59,320
Sorry.

346
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:05,840
That came out of nowhere.

347
00:22:11,190 --> 00:22:12,640
You were as stubborn as a mule

348
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:15,560
in class yesterday.

349
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:17,920
I was being impulsive.

350
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:20,190
If it weren't for you,
I would have made a huge mistake.

351
00:22:24,560 --> 00:22:26,160
I'm sorry you got hurt because of me.

352
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:32,160
Just a "sorry" and that's it?

353
00:22:32,910 --> 00:22:33,950
What more do you want?

354
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,640
I want you to make it up to me.

355
00:24:05,320 --> 00:24:06,160
What are you doing?

356
00:24:06,280 --> 00:24:07,800
Who said you could go through my stuff?

357
00:24:08,190 --> 00:24:08,640
Huh?

358
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:11,190
I just wanted to help you tidy up.

359
00:24:11,190 --> 00:24:12,309
I didn't mean to touch that.

360
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:14,090
That doesn't mean
you can go through my things.

361
00:24:15,430 --> 00:24:16,840
You don't owe me anything anymore.

362
00:24:16,950 --> 00:24:17,510
Leave.

363
00:24:19,470 --> 00:24:20,270
Get out of here!

364
00:24:52,470 --> 00:24:53,270
Qiao Qingyu.

365
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:55,430
Morning.

366
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:10,910
Don't just wander off!

367
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:25,600
Hey.

368
00:25:27,910 --> 00:25:29,800
What a coincidence, Qiao Qingyu.

369
00:25:38,040 --> 00:25:38,800
What do you want?

370
00:25:40,190 --> 00:25:41,670
Still want that letter?

371
00:25:41,910 --> 00:25:42,800
What letter?

372
00:25:44,470 --> 00:25:46,710
The one from your dear old classmate,

373
00:25:47,080 --> 00:25:49,040
Niao Mingkai.

374
00:25:49,120 --> 00:25:50,560
I kept forgetting to bring it to you.

375
00:25:51,230 --> 00:25:52,840
Meet me by the big tree after school.

376
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:54,430
If you don't show up,

377
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,400
I'll assume you don't want it anymore.

378
00:25:56,670 --> 00:25:57,430
I'll get rid of it.

379
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:58,270
It's up to you.

380
00:25:58,270 --> 00:25:58,510
Sheng.

381
00:25:58,510 --> 00:26:01,040
Hurry up. We're free to do what we want
after we finish the laps.

382
00:26:01,040 --> 00:26:01,560
Come on.

383
00:26:02,840 --> 00:26:03,910
Don't stand me up!

384
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:25,510
Come on up.

385
00:26:29,280 --> 00:26:30,320
Don't you want your letter?

386
00:26:36,950 --> 00:26:37,750
My letter?

387
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:41,160
Close your eyes.

388
00:26:41,990 --> 00:26:42,670
Why?

389
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:44,640
Just do it.

390
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,320
What next?

391
00:26:50,710 --> 00:26:53,230
Did you hear that sound?

392
00:27:04,670 --> 00:27:07,230
Actually, this tree can talk.

393
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:09,600
It's saying,

394
00:27:15,910 --> 00:27:16,800
"I'm sorry."

395
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,640
You're messing with me.

396
00:27:22,710 --> 00:27:23,800
I'm not.

397
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:28,750
I shouldn't have
snapped at you yesterday.

398
00:27:29,990 --> 00:27:30,800
I'm sorry.

399
00:27:35,470 --> 00:27:37,040
Those records and albums

400
00:27:37,040 --> 00:27:38,160
were my mom's.

401
00:27:39,040 --> 00:27:40,360
This place used to be

402
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,360
our secret hideout.

403
00:27:45,190 --> 00:27:46,470
Want to hear my story?

404
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,160
My parents divorced

405
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:01,040
when I was really young.

406
00:28:02,910 --> 00:28:04,230
I was raised by my grandfather.

407
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:06,840
The summer
before the high school entrance exam,

408
00:28:08,430 --> 00:28:09,510
my grandpa passed away too.

409
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:12,710
After that,

410
00:28:14,320 --> 00:28:15,600
I became nothing but a burden.

411
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,990
That's why I always felt like

412
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,510
my whole existence was a mistake.

413
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:26,800
So you see, Qiao Qingyu,

414
00:28:27,320 --> 00:28:28,880
you're not the only one with a weakness.

415
00:28:34,670 --> 00:28:36,360
Why are you telling me all this?

416
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,560
I just felt like it.

417
00:28:45,270 --> 00:28:45,950
Ming Sheng.

418
00:28:46,230 --> 00:28:46,750
Hm?

419
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:52,400
You're not that bad.

420
00:29:25,360 --> 00:29:25,950
I'm home.

421
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,080
Oh.

422
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:30,710
Me too.

423
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:33,080
Well, I'm going up now.

424
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:33,670
Mm.

425
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:36,320
Qiao Qingyu.

426
00:29:44,152 --> 00:29:44,942
Your letter.

427
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,120
I finally remembered to bring it.

428
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:50,360
(To: Qiao Qingyu, From: Niao Mingkai)

429
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,910
Will you write back to him?

430
00:29:55,520 --> 00:29:56,510
Don't get the wrong idea.

431
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:58,990
Final exams are coming up.

432
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:00,750
Wouldn't want you getting distracted.

433
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:04,160
I'm going home.

434
00:30:07,950 --> 00:30:09,270
I'm not going to write him back.

435
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:38,670
Qingyu.

436
00:30:38,950 --> 00:30:40,360
You should've knocked, Mom.

437
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:42,750
Oh, I forgot about that.

438
00:30:43,040 --> 00:30:44,400
Skip school tomorrow.

439
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,430
I got you a day off.

440
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,510
Come with me to take care of something.

441
00:30:47,510 --> 00:30:48,230
What is it?

442
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:49,880
You'll know tomorrow.

443
00:31:00,311 --> 00:31:04,690
(Huanzhou Bus Station)

444
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:07,040
Come on.

445
00:31:07,190 --> 00:31:08,230
Where are we going?

446
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:10,750
We're going back to our hometown
to change your name.

447
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,470
Why?

448
00:31:12,910 --> 00:31:13,640
People are saying

449
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:15,320
the names Qingyu and Beiyu are unlucky.

450
00:31:15,320 --> 00:31:16,230
We need to change them.

451
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:18,000
I don't want you
ending up like your sister.

452
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:18,440
Change it,

453
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,840
and you won't have any more trouble.

454
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:20,510
I'm not going!

455
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:20,880
Qingyu...

456
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:22,120
I don't want to change my name!

457
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:23,230
You don't get a say in this!

458
00:31:23,230 --> 00:31:24,750
I'm not going! I don't want to!

459
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:25,640
Behave!

460
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:26,950
I don't want to go!

461
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:28,080
Look!

462
00:31:28,080 --> 00:31:29,480
We can talk about this, ma'am.

463
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,640
She's my daughter! Let me go!

464
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,360
She's my daughter!

465
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:32,320
Please let go of her.

466
00:31:32,320 --> 00:31:33,080
She's my daughter!

467
00:31:33,080 --> 00:31:33,720
Let go.

468
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,560
What are you doing?

469
00:31:34,560 --> 00:31:35,360
Be civil.

470
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:37,560
She kept dragging that girl along.

471
00:31:37,750 --> 00:31:39,910
I could tell
the girl didn't want to go with her.

472
00:31:40,120 --> 00:31:41,270
My name is Li Fanghao.

473
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,750
She's Qiao Qingyu.

474
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:43,440
She's my daughter.

475
00:31:43,510 --> 00:31:45,480
I was just trying to take her back
to her hometown.

476
00:31:45,480 --> 00:31:46,750
Is she your mother, Miss?

477
00:31:48,470 --> 00:31:49,560
She's ignoring you.

478
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:50,800
She doesn't want to talk to you.

479
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:51,920
What's up with this old woman?

480
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:52,990
Qiao Qingyu, say something!

481
00:31:52,990 --> 00:31:54,560
Why are you hiding your face
with a mask?

482
00:31:54,670 --> 00:31:55,440
Ashamed to be seen?

483
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:55,950
That's right.

484
00:31:55,950 --> 00:31:57,670
I think she might be a human trafficker.

485
00:31:57,670 --> 00:31:58,670
I'm not a trafficker!

486
00:31:58,670 --> 00:31:59,600
Qiao Qingyu!

487
00:31:59,670 --> 00:32:00,880
Then why won't she talk to you?

488
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:02,190
What do you think you're doing?

489
00:32:02,800 --> 00:32:03,510
Qingyu!

490
00:32:04,950 --> 00:32:06,040
Explain yourself.

491
00:32:07,600 --> 00:32:09,160
She doesn't even want
to bother with you.

492
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,480
Don't you dare try anything!

493
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:12,840
Explain yourself, woman.

494
00:32:13,470 --> 00:32:14,950
Explain yourself first!

495
00:32:14,950 --> 00:32:15,950
Qiao Qingyu!

496
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,240
Qiao Qingyu.

497
00:32:40,970 --> 00:32:41,970
What was that back there?

498
00:32:44,530 --> 00:32:45,560
I asked you a question.

499
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:48,650
What were you thinking?

500
00:32:49,890 --> 00:32:51,520
Did you think
once the police took me away,

501
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:52,250
you'd be free?

502
00:32:52,250 --> 00:32:52,970
That's enough.

503
00:32:52,970 --> 00:32:53,370
Answer me!

504
00:32:53,370 --> 00:32:54,240
All right, all right.

505
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,560
She knows what she did wrong.

506
00:32:55,730 --> 00:32:57,080
Come on. Apologize to your mother.

507
00:32:57,080 --> 00:32:58,130
Say you won't do it again.

508
00:32:58,130 --> 00:32:59,690
I won't apologize.
I did nothing wrong.

509
00:32:59,970 --> 00:33:01,130
Qiao Qingyu, you listen to me.

510
00:33:01,410 --> 00:33:03,040
As long as I'm alive,
you'll do as I say.

511
00:33:03,130 --> 00:33:04,080
I'm your mother.

512
00:33:04,130 --> 00:33:05,080
Enough.

513
00:33:05,410 --> 00:33:06,610
There's a knife in the kitchen.

514
00:33:06,610 --> 00:33:07,570
Go on. Stab me.

515
00:33:07,570 --> 00:33:09,090
Kill me, and you can do what you want.

516
00:33:09,090 --> 00:33:10,250
You'll be free once I'm dead!

517
00:33:10,250 --> 00:33:11,290
You disrespected me first.

518
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:12,280
You...

519
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:14,530
Qiao Qingyu!

520
00:33:14,530 --> 00:33:15,810
Calm down. Let's talk about this.

521
00:33:15,810 --> 00:33:17,210
Your father and I worked tirelessly

522
00:33:17,210 --> 00:33:18,040
to send you to school!

523
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:18,370
Get out!

524
00:33:18,370 --> 00:33:19,450
Don't come back if you dare.

525
00:33:20,280 --> 00:33:21,450
You think I owe you respect?

526
00:33:21,450 --> 00:33:22,280
Enough. Calm down.

527
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:22,810
That's enough!

528
00:33:22,810 --> 00:33:23,850
She can do this to me today.

529
00:33:23,850 --> 00:33:25,210
She can do the same to you tomorrow!

530
00:33:25,210 --> 00:33:26,760
Just talk to her.
You shouldn't force her.

531
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:27,720
You're all defending her!

532
00:33:29,560 --> 00:33:30,410
You...

533
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:32,450
She has a point.

534
00:33:33,450 --> 00:33:34,210
Look.

535
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:36,040
You should respect her wishes too.

536
00:33:36,210 --> 00:33:37,370
She's not a child anymore.

537
00:33:37,560 --> 00:33:38,890
Can't you just ease up a little?

538
00:33:39,720 --> 00:33:40,410
Qiao Lusheng,

539
00:33:40,570 --> 00:33:41,930
how many times did you ever step up

540
00:33:42,560 --> 00:33:43,450
as a father?

541
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:45,930
Were you ever even there for them?

542
00:33:49,370 --> 00:33:50,890
Because you never took responsibility.

543
00:33:51,050 --> 00:33:52,690
Because you always
passed everything to me.

544
00:33:52,690 --> 00:33:53,810
I had to take on everything.

545
00:33:59,970 --> 00:34:00,930
Beiyu...

546
00:34:00,930 --> 00:34:02,450
I couldn't raise Beiyu by myself.

547
00:34:02,450 --> 00:34:04,520
Her grandparents did,
but they didn't care about her.

548
00:34:04,530 --> 00:34:07,170
And every time I saw her,
I couldn't bring myself to discipline her.

549
00:34:08,370 --> 00:34:10,290
And look how that turned out.

550
00:34:13,290 --> 00:34:15,050
I can't just stand by

551
00:34:15,050 --> 00:34:16,410
and let Qingyu turn out the same.

552
00:34:25,640 --> 00:34:26,930
This is about the kids.

553
00:34:26,930 --> 00:34:28,640
Why are you suddenly blaming my parents?

554
00:34:30,250 --> 00:34:31,850
It's not like
they didn't raise the child.

555
00:34:31,850 --> 00:34:33,480
They tried their best.

556
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:34,850
They brought her up.

557
00:34:37,930 --> 00:34:38,810
Qiao Lusheng!

558
00:34:39,890 --> 00:34:43,000
Did I ask them to raise my child?

559
00:34:45,640 --> 00:34:47,890
They took her from me!

560
00:34:48,200 --> 00:34:49,730
You were in on it too!

561
00:34:53,370 --> 00:34:55,640
All for your pride, your image,

562
00:34:55,640 --> 00:34:56,850
your vanity.

563
00:34:57,250 --> 00:34:59,160
I never should've listened to you.

564
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:03,850
I should've taken Beiyu
and disappeared far, far away...

