00:35:26,250 --> 00:35:27,080
Take it.

566
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:36,080
Getting a name change
isn't the worst idea.

567
00:35:37,250 --> 00:35:39,770
Might as well pick something

568
00:35:39,770 --> 00:35:42,810
that sounds nicer.

569
00:35:42,810 --> 00:35:44,450
We can both change our names.

570
00:35:44,450 --> 00:35:46,050
Something in the same vein.

571
00:35:46,050 --> 00:35:47,330
That way, people will still know

572
00:35:47,330 --> 00:35:48,890
we're siblings when they hear our names.

573
00:36:06,600 --> 00:36:07,730
Students.

574
00:36:07,730 --> 00:36:08,930
Some students

575
00:36:08,930 --> 00:36:11,250
did not attend

576
00:36:11,250 --> 00:36:13,000
yesterday's anti-bullying seminar

577
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:15,040
organized by the school.

578
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:16,560
I've marked that down.

579
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:18,370
Come explain yourselves
after the meeting.

580
00:36:18,370 --> 00:36:19,330
Class Representative,

581
00:36:19,330 --> 00:36:20,690
please hand out the winter homework

582
00:36:20,690 --> 00:36:21,600
and report cards later.

583
00:36:22,080 --> 00:36:23,090
I won't nag here,

584
00:36:23,090 --> 00:36:25,080
but make sure you finish
your homework on time.

585
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:26,810
And be safe
if you're going out over break.

586
00:36:27,160 --> 00:36:29,600
Have a good winter break.

587
00:37:29,330 --> 00:37:30,850
You're on winter break now?

588
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,250
Sorry.

589
00:37:33,770 --> 00:37:35,770
It's because
I went asking around about Hei

590
00:37:35,890 --> 00:37:37,040
that he came after you.

591
00:37:38,330 --> 00:37:39,410
It wasn't your fault.

592
00:37:39,410 --> 00:37:41,010
I was the one who chose to look for him.

593
00:37:41,410 --> 00:37:42,810
And it's already over.

594
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:44,930
Was he the one you were looking for?

595
00:37:54,520 --> 00:37:56,250
After Beiyu dropped out,

596
00:37:56,250 --> 00:37:58,970
your parents came to pack her things.

597
00:37:58,970 --> 00:38:00,600
They went through everything.

598
00:38:01,600 --> 00:38:03,080
But Beiyu was good at hiding.

599
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:04,250
They didn't find anything.

600
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,040
I think

601
00:38:06,040 --> 00:38:08,600
you might find a clue in this.

602
00:38:29,010 --> 00:38:30,770
(Report of HIV Antibody
Confirmatory Testing)

603
00:38:30,770 --> 00:38:32,010
(I loved him. He was my first.)

604
00:38:41,219 --> 00:38:43,699
(China is experiencing
its worst cold wave in a century.)

605
00:38:43,810 --> 00:38:45,250
(Since mid-last month,)

606
00:38:45,250 --> 00:38:47,560
(heavy snow has hit central
and eastern mountain regions,)

607
00:38:48,250 --> 00:38:49,810
(with widespread freezing conditions.)

608
00:38:50,010 --> 00:38:52,290
(Multiple highways across the province
have been shut down,)

609
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:54,520
(and transportation
has been severely affected.)

610
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:55,810
(Experts predict)

611
00:38:55,810 --> 00:38:58,600
(the cold wave will continue
through the Chinese New Year.)

612
00:39:12,810 --> 00:39:15,040
Qingyu, Mom gave you this.

613
00:39:22,080 --> 00:39:26,330
I'm not hungry too, Mom.

614
00:39:46,010 --> 00:39:47,600
The bus is having
some mechanical issues.

615
00:39:47,600 --> 00:39:48,730
I'll get out and take a look.

616
00:39:49,560 --> 00:39:51,040
Can you fix it?

617
00:39:51,410 --> 00:39:53,160
Don't rush me. I'll check.

618
00:40:01,370 --> 00:40:03,410
The bus broke down.
It'll take about an hour to fix.

619
00:40:03,410 --> 00:40:04,890
There are roughly ten li left ahead.

620
00:40:04,890 --> 00:40:06,810
If you're in a hurry,
you can start walking.

621
00:40:06,810 --> 00:40:07,640
Give us a refund.

622
00:40:07,810 --> 00:40:08,330
No refunds.

623
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,200
What if he can't fix the bus?

624
00:40:18,730 --> 00:40:19,410
He said

625
00:40:19,410 --> 00:40:20,810
it'll be fixed in an hour.

626
00:40:21,370 --> 00:40:23,080
It's almost ten li back from here.

627
00:40:23,090 --> 00:40:24,370
How long would that take on foot?

628
00:40:25,210 --> 00:40:26,040
We'd freeze to death.

629
00:40:27,010 --> 00:40:28,480
We have all these things with us too.

630
00:40:42,850 --> 00:40:44,610
I think I'll have

631
00:40:44,610 --> 00:40:45,770
that tea egg after all, Mom.

632
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:47,730
I'm feeling a little hungry now.

633
00:40:58,640 --> 00:40:59,730
Save one for your sister.

634
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:02,450
She doesn't want it.

635
00:41:08,410 --> 00:41:10,000
Dad! Mom!

636
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:11,330
We're back.

637
00:41:11,330 --> 00:41:12,160
Dad.

638
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:15,160
You're finally back, Lusheng.
We were worried about you.

639
00:41:15,160 --> 00:41:16,770
The bus broke down on the way,

640
00:41:16,770 --> 00:41:17,810
so we were delayed a bit.

641
00:41:19,410 --> 00:41:20,640
You must be freezing, Yu.

642
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:22,560
Is the ginger soup ready?

643
00:41:22,810 --> 00:41:23,680
Yes.

644
00:41:24,130 --> 00:41:25,000
I bought this for you.

645
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,290
Just leave it on the table.

646
00:41:26,290 --> 00:41:27,200
Here's the ginger soup.

647
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:28,290
You're all back.

648
00:41:28,290 --> 00:41:29,810
I'll get some rest, then.

649
00:41:29,810 --> 00:41:31,290
Yes, of course. Get some rest.

650
00:41:31,290 --> 00:41:33,330
- It's terribly cold.
- Come on.

651
00:41:33,370 --> 00:41:34,330
Have some ginger soup.

652
00:41:34,850 --> 00:41:36,160
Drink up.

653
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:37,040
I'll do it, Mom.

654
00:41:37,330 --> 00:41:38,730
Hurry.

655
00:41:38,970 --> 00:41:39,640
Yanfen.

656
00:41:40,290 --> 00:41:41,970
How's Jinrui's wedding coming along?

657
00:41:41,970 --> 00:41:43,770
They've already registered
their marriage.

658
00:41:45,290 --> 00:41:46,080
Good, good.

659
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:46,770
Thanks, Grandma.

660
00:41:46,930 --> 00:41:48,600
I'm cold too, Grandma.

661
00:41:48,930 --> 00:41:50,000
You have hands, don't you?

662
00:41:50,210 --> 00:41:51,810
My daughter-in-law isn't going anywhere.

663
00:41:52,810 --> 00:41:54,250
She's beautiful,

664
00:41:54,250 --> 00:41:56,930
well-educated,

665
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:58,560
and an only child too.

666
00:41:59,160 --> 00:42:01,810
She'll be able to support Jinrui.

667
00:42:02,680 --> 00:42:03,330
Also,

668
00:42:03,410 --> 00:42:06,080
they're city folks
and didn't ask for a dowry.

669
00:42:07,410 --> 00:42:08,970
She's perfect in every way.

670
00:42:09,080 --> 00:42:09,560
That's good.

671
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:11,290
For Jinrui to marry Xiaoyun

672
00:42:11,680 --> 00:42:14,080
is a blessing for our family.

673
00:42:14,330 --> 00:42:15,120
That's good to hear.

674
00:42:15,410 --> 00:42:17,890
You make it sound like
we're the ones marrying up.

675
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:21,560
My grandson was the county's
top scorer on the NCEE.

676
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:23,290
Forget one Xiaoyun.

677
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:24,810
He can marry ten of them

678
00:42:25,040 --> 00:42:26,330
if he wants.

679
00:42:27,450 --> 00:42:28,200
That's right.

680
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:32,810
The Secretary added Jinrui and Xiaoyun
into the family genealogy book

681
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:34,330
a few days ago.

682
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:35,680
These days,

683
00:42:35,930 --> 00:42:38,040
it's Jinrui who's carrying

684
00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:40,730
the reputation
of the entire Qiao family.

685
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:42,120
Grandma,

686
00:42:42,450 --> 00:42:44,850
when will Qingyu and I be added
to the genealogy?

687
00:42:45,600 --> 00:42:47,160
Once you get married,

688
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:49,730
the Secretary will add your name in.

689
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:51,640
What about Qingyu?

690
00:42:52,200 --> 00:42:53,450
She's a girl.

691
00:42:53,890 --> 00:42:55,520
She'll marry
into another family someday.

692
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:56,600
That's right.

693
00:42:58,200 --> 00:42:59,640
I'll go put away my bags.

694
00:43:00,330 --> 00:43:00,730
All right.

695
00:43:01,520 --> 00:43:02,850
Sort your things out.

696
00:43:04,450 --> 00:43:05,640
Have a seat, Lusheng.

697
00:43:05,890 --> 00:43:06,250
Okay.

698
00:43:06,250 --> 00:43:06,610
Sit down.

699
00:43:06,610 --> 00:43:07,290
You too, Yanfen.

700
00:43:07,290 --> 00:43:07,690
All right.

701
00:43:07,690 --> 00:43:08,810
I'd like some more, Grandma.

702
00:43:09,250 --> 00:43:10,890
Eat up, Yu.

703
00:43:11,930 --> 00:43:13,480
I'm good. You guys have more.

704
00:43:46,780 --> 00:43:49,000
♪Maybe♪

705
00:43:50,860 --> 00:43:56,260
♪The more I care,
the more I tread carefully♪

706
00:43:57,950 --> 00:44:03,300
♪Counting the distance between us♪

707
00:44:04,200 --> 00:44:10,460
♪Just one step away from reaching♪

708
00:44:15,460 --> 00:44:17,750
♪The future♪

709
00:44:19,450 --> 00:44:25,070
♪Time will unveil this mystery♪

710
00:44:26,650 --> 00:44:32,010
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

711
00:44:32,860 --> 00:44:39,170
♪But one that never expires♪

712
00:44:41,490 --> 00:44:46,540
♪Turns out, all my thoughts♪

713
00:44:46,640 --> 00:44:50,950
♪Spell your name♪

714
00:44:51,240 --> 00:44:57,250
♪The one and only stubbornness
in my heart♪

715
00:44:57,470 --> 00:45:00,780
♪From the very first glance♪

716
00:45:01,130 --> 00:45:05,200
♪I started painting
what our future would look like♪

717
00:45:05,200 --> 00:45:11,470
♪That's when the dream began
to feel real♪

718
00:45:11,470 --> 00:45:15,130
♪Turns out♪

719
00:45:15,450 --> 00:45:19,510
♪Your heart had a place for me too♪

720
00:45:19,910 --> 00:45:25,890
♪Cradling the same story we both knew♪

721
00:45:26,160 --> 00:45:29,820
♪Thankfully, we were naïve enough♪

722
00:45:29,820 --> 00:45:33,360
♪And brave just in time♪

723
00:45:33,360 --> 00:45:40,340
♪To make sure our moments
weren't lost to time♪
